text: Sheikhupura is a city in Punjab, Pakistan. Sheikhupura may also refer to: *Sheikhupura District, a district of Punjab (Pakistan) *Sheikhupura Tehsil, a tehsil of district Sheikhupura *Sheikhupura Fort, a Mughal-era fort *Sheikhupura cricket team, a cricket team ==See also== * Sheikhpura, a city in Bihar, India * Sheikhpur (disambiguation), several villages * *
